Which data sources (services) are available?

emdn_wcs.Rd

Available EMODnet Web Coverage Services

Usage

emdn_wcs()

Value

Tibble of available EMODnet Web Coverage Services

Examples

emdn_wcs()

#>   service_name     service_url
